llm_generators.prompt_template:
You are analyzing a performance report for a game level/scene. Generate a concise executive summary (2-3 paragraphs) based on this data:

Location: {context.location}
Total samples: {stats.count}

Draw Calls:
- Mean: {stats.draws.mean}, Median: {stats.draws.median}
- P90: {stats.draws.p90}, P95: {stats.draws.p95}, P99: {stats.draws.p99}
- CV (variability): {stats.draws.cv}%
- Trend: {stats.trends.draws.direction}

Triangles:
- Mean: {stats.tris.mean}, Median: {stats.tris.median}
- P90: {stats.tris.p90}, P95: {stats.tris.p95}, P99: {stats.tris.p99}
- CV (variability): {stats.tris.cv}%
- Trend: {stats.trends.tris.direction}

Analyze the provided data table to understand performance patterns.

Write a professional executive summary covering:
{categories}

Use HTML paragraph tags (<p>) for formatting. Be concise, data-driven, and reference the enhanced statistics.
